message.content:
Based on public knowledge and typical formulations, here's an estimate of the ingredients in Gorilla Mode Pre-Workout by Gorilla Mind:

1. Beta-Alanine
2. Citrulline Malate
3. Creatine Monohydrate
4. Nitric Oxide Boosters (Beetroot Juice, L-Citrulline, L-Arginine)
5. Branched-Chain Amino Acids (BCAAs) (L-Leucine, L-Isoleucine, L-Valine)
6. L-Tyrosine
7. L-Glutamine
8. L-Carnitine
9. L-Ornithine
10. Glycerol Powder
11. Coconut Water Powder
12. Natural Flavors
13. Sweeteners (Sucralose, Acesulfame Potassium)
14. Calcium Silicate (Anti-Caking Agent)
15. Silicon Dioxide (Anti-Caking Agent)

Please note that this is an estimate based on publicly available information and may not accurately reflect the actual ingredients or their proportions in the product.
